SubmitterDescription.SubmitterName: International Standards For Cytogenomic Arrays Consortium (ISCA)

SampleDescription.Description: Mosaic - A limited chromosome study confirmed the direct duplication within a single chromosome 1 in 7 out of 10 metaphases. FISH studies using a probe within the duplicated interval (RP11-273A3) confirmed this duplication in 70% of metaphases and 75.5% of interphase nuclei from a PHA-stimulated culture as well as in 69.0% of interphase nuclei from a direct unstimulated sample

ClinicalAssertion.StudyDescription: Copy number variation identified through the course of routine clinical cytogenomic testing in postnatal populations, with clinical assertions as classified by the original submitter.
